flowchart TD
    Start([HTTP Request]) --> Server[Express Server<br/>Port 5000]

    Server --> Middleware{Middleware<br/>Pipeline}

    Middleware --> Compression[Compression]
    Compression --> Static{Static Files?}
    Static -->|/assets| Assets[Equipment Images]
    Static -->|/uploads| Uploads[Activity Attachments]
    Static -->|No| Session[Session Store<br/>PostgreSQL]

    Assets --> Response([Response])
    Uploads --> Response

    Session --> Passport[Passport.js Init]
    Passport --> BodyParser{Body Parser}

    BodyParser -->|Stripe Webhook| RawBody[Raw Body]
    BodyParser -->|PDF Upload| Skip[Skip Parsing]
    BodyParser -->|Standard| JSON[JSON Parser<br/>1MB Limit]

    RawBody --> RouteMatch{Route<br/>Matching}
    Skip --> RouteMatch
    JSON --> RouteMatch

    RouteMatch -->|/health| Health[Health Check ✓]
    RouteMatch -->|/api/webhooks/stripe| StripeWebhook[Stripe Webhook Handler]
    RouteMatch -->|/api/webhooks/textline| TextlineWebhook[Textline Webhook]
    RouteMatch -->|Auth Routes| AuthRoutes[Authentication]
    RouteMatch -->|API Routes| APIRoutes[API Endpoints]

    Health --> Response
    StripeWebhook --> Response
    TextlineWebhook --> Response

    AuthRoutes --> AuthType{Auth<br/>System}

    AuthType -->|Employee Portal| PortalAuth[Passport Local Strategy<br/>Session-Based]
    AuthType -->|CRM| CRMAuth[Token-Based Auth<br/>8-Hour Sessions]
    AuthType -->|Admin API| AdminAuth[Bearer Token<br/>+ API Key]

    PortalAuth --> PortalSession{Session<br/>Valid?}
    PortalSession -->|No| Auth401[401 Unauthorized]
    PortalSession -->|Yes| PortalRole{Role<br/>Check}
    PortalRole -->|Admin| PortalRoutes
    PortalRole -->|Employee| PortalRoutes

    CRMAuth --> CRMSession{Session<br/>Valid?}
    CRMSession -->|No| Auth401
    CRMSession -->|Yes| CRMRole{Role<br/>Hierarchy}

    CRMRole -->|owner: 100| CRMRoutes
    CRMRole -->|manager: 80| CRMRoutes
    CRMRole -->|dispatcher: 60| CRMRoutes
    CRMRole -->|sales: 40| CRMRoutes
    CRMRole -->|tech: 20| CRMRoutes
    CRMRole -->|viewer: 10| CRMRoutes
    CRMRole -->|Insufficient| Auth403[403 Forbidden]

    AdminAuth --> AdminValid{Token/Key<br/>Valid?}
    AdminValid -->|No| Auth401
    AdminValid -->|Yes| AdminRoutes

    APIRoutes --> Category{Route<br/>Category}

    Category -->|Customer Portal| PortalRoutes[Customer Portal<br/>8 endpoints]
    Category -->|Mobile App| MobileRoutes[Mobile Tech App<br/>10+ endpoints]
    Category -->|CRM Core| CRMRoutes[CRM Modules<br/>200+ endpoints]
    Category -->|Integrations| IntegrationRoutes[External APIs<br/>60+ endpoints]
    Category -->|Public| PublicRoutes[Public Access<br/>Invoice/Quote View]

    PortalRoutes --> PortalFeatures{Feature}
    PortalFeatures -->|Auth| PortalAuthOps[Login/Logout]
    PortalFeatures -->|Dashboard| PortalDashboard[Customer Dashboard]
    PortalFeatures -->|Invoices| PortalInvoices[View Invoices]
    PortalFeatures -->|Quotes| PortalQuotes[View Quotes]
    PortalFeatures -->|Agreements| PortalAgreements[Maintenance Plans]
    PortalFeatures -->|History| ServiceHistory[Service History]

    MobileRoutes --> MobileFeatures{Feature}
    MobileFeatures -->|Work Orders| MobileWO[Tech Work Orders]
    MobileFeatures -->|Time Tracking| TimeTrack[Clock In/Out]
    MobileFeatures -->|Messaging| MobileMsg[Tech Messages]
    MobileFeatures -->|Performance| TechPerf[Performance Stats]

    CRMRoutes --> CRMModules{CRM Module}

    CRMModules -->|Customers| CustomerOps[Customers Module<br/>15+ endpoints]
    CRMModules -->|Accounts| AccountOps[Commercial Accounts<br/>Multi-site Management]
    CRMModules -->|Properties| PropertyOps[Property Management<br/>Equipment Tracking]
    CRMModules -->|Work Orders| WorkOrderOps[Work Order Lifecycle<br/>20+ endpoints]
    CRMModules -->|Projects| ProjectOps[Project Pipeline<br/>Activities & Timeline]
    CRMModules -->|Quotes| QuoteOps[AI Quote Generation<br/>20+ endpoints]
    CRMModules -->|Invoices| InvoiceOps[Invoice Management<br/>15+ endpoints]
    CRMModules -->|Agreements| AgreementOps[Maintenance Agreements<br/>Tasks & Visits]
    CRMModules -->|Messaging| MessagingOps[SMS/Textline<br/>12+ endpoints]
    CRMModules -->|Checklists| ChecklistOps[Service Call Checklists<br/>AI Summaries]
    CRMModules -->|Goals| GoalsOps[Performance Goals<br/>Tracking Dashboard]
    CRMModules -->|Follow-ups| FollowUpOps[Follow-up Management]
    CRMModules -->|Users| UserOps[User & Role Management]

    IntegrationRoutes --> Integration{Integration<br/>Type}

    Integration -->|QuickBooks| QBOps[QuickBooks Online<br/>OAuth + Sync<br/>30+ endpoints]
    Integration -->|FieldEdge| FEOps[FieldEdge Customers<br/>Google Sheets Sync]
    Integration -->|Bouncie| BouncieOps[Vehicle Tracking<br/>OAuth + GPS<br/>8 endpoints]
    Integration -->|Pricebook| PricebookOps[Package Management<br/>Google Sheets Sync]
    Integration -->|Stripe| StripeOps[Payment Processing<br/>Subscription Billing]
    Integration -->|Weather| WeatherOps[Weather API<br/>Impact Analysis]
    Integration -->|Voice| VoiceOps[OpenAI Whisper<br/>Transcription]

    CustomerOps --> DBOps[Database Operations]
    AccountOps --> DBOps
    PropertyOps --> DBOps
    WorkOrderOps --> DBOps
    ProjectOps --> DBOps
    QuoteOps --> AIService[OpenAI Service]
    InvoiceOps --> DBOps
    AgreementOps --> DBOps
    MessagingOps --> TextlineService[Textline API]
    ChecklistOps --> AIService
    GoalsOps --> DBOps
    FollowUpOps --> DBOps
    UserOps --> DBOps

    PortalAuthOps --> DBOps
    PortalDashboard --> DBOps
    PortalInvoices --> DBOps
    PortalQuotes --> DBOps
    PortalAgreements --> DBOps
    ServiceHistory --> DBOps

    MobileWO --> DBOps
    TimeTrack --> DBOps
    MobileMsg --> DBOps
    TechPerf --> DBOps

    QBOps --> QBService[QuickBooks Service<br/>OAuth Flow<br/>Customer/Invoice Sync]
    FEOps --> FEService[FieldEdge Service<br/>5-min Auto Refresh]
    BouncieOps --> BouncieService[Bouncie Service<br/>OAuth + Location Sync]
    PricebookOps --> PricebookService[Package Sync Service<br/>1-min Interval]
    StripeOps --> StripeService[Stripe Service<br/>Webhook Processing]
    WeatherOps --> WeatherService[Weather API Client]
    VoiceOps --> AIService

    PublicRoutes --> PublicOps{Public Feature}
    PublicOps -->|Invoice View| PublicInvoice[View Invoice by Token]
    PublicOps -->|Quote View| PublicQuote[View Quote by Token]

    PublicInvoice --> DBOps
    PublicQuote --> DBOps

    AIService --> OpenAI[OpenAI API<br/>GPT-3.5-turbo<br/>Whisper<br/>Embeddings]
    TextlineService --> Textline[Textline SMS API]
    QBService --> QuickBooks[QuickBooks Online API]
    FEService --> GoogleSheets[Google Sheets API]
    BouncieService --> BouncieAPI[Bouncie API]
    PricebookService --> GoogleSheets
    StripeService --> StripeAPI[Stripe API]
    WeatherService --> WeatherAPI[Weather API]

    DBOps --> DB[(PostgreSQL<br/>Neon<br/>Drizzle ORM)]

    DB --> AuditLog[crm_audit_log<br/>Action Tracking]

    DBOps --> EmailService{Email<br/>Needed?}
    EmailService -->|Quote Send| ResendEmail[Resend API<br/>Quote Template]
    EmailService -->|Invoice Send| ResendEmail
    EmailService -->|No| ResponseData[Format Response Data]

    ResendEmail --> ResponseData
    OpenAI --> ResponseData
    Textline --> ResponseData
    QuickBooks --> ResponseData
    BouncieAPI --> ResponseData
    StripeAPI --> ResponseData
    WeatherAPI --> ResponseData
    AuditLog --> ResponseData

    ResponseData --> Cache{Cache<br/>Available?}
    Cache -->|Analytics| CacheHit[30s TTL Cache]
    Cache -->|No| ResponseFinal

    CacheHit --> ResponseFinal[Return JSON Response]
    ResponseFinal --> Response

    Auth401 --> Response
    Auth403 --> Response

    Server -.->|Background| BackgroundJobs[Background Services]

    BackgroundJobs --> BG1[QuickBooks Sync Scheduler]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG2[FieldEdge 5-min Refresh]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG3[Pricebook 1-min Sync]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG4[Agreement Renewals]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG5[Maintenance Reminders]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG6[Review Request Automation]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG7[Bouncie Location Sync]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG8[Weather Updates]
    BackgroundJobs --> BG9[Stripe Product Backfill]

    BG1 --> DB
    BG2 --> DB
    BG3 --> DB
    BG4 --> DB
    BG5 --> DB
    BG6 --> DB
    BG7 --> DB
    BG8 --> DB
    BG9 --> DB

    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style Response fill:#e1f5ff
    style Server fill:#fff3cd
    style DB fill:#d4edda
    style OpenAI fill:#f8d7da
    style QuickBooks fill:#f8d7da
    style StripeAPI fill:#f8d7da
    style Textline fill:#f8d7da
    style BackgroundJobs fill:#e2e3e5
